<strong>5. Finally build your campaign to tie it all together.</strong> You’ll add your form as the source where you are collecting leads, then you’ll build out the email to send to them, and the landing page you want them to land on when they opt-in. Your campaign flow might look something like below:

<img class="thumbnail aligncenter wp-image-754 size-full" src="https://www.mautic.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/opt_in_campaign.png" alt="Campaign structure for double opt-in email" width="519" height="452" />
<h3>Here’s a step-by-step breakdown of a double opt-in email campaign:</h3>
