What happens when that data can be changed by either application? Imagine a situation where you’re taking lead information from your website, and storing it in Mautic. But you also have another application that you want to house the information. You could use <a href="https://www.mautic.org/blog/how-to-use-the-mautic-rest-api/">Mautic’s REST API</a> and continually go and fetch new information, merge with any data you’ve curated on your own, and maintain a synced set of data that way.

