<!--more-->
<h3><a href="https://www.mautic.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/keyboard-shortcuts.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-1994 size-large" src="https://www.mautic.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/keyboard-shortcuts-1024x648.jpg" alt="mautic keyboard shortcuts" width="720" height="456" /></a>Mautic Keyboard Shortcuts</h3>
