Every <a href="http://www.instagram.com/trymautic">Instagram</a> post I used <a href="https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/movehorizons/">#movehorizons</a> and I loved the fact that I actually believed we could. I’m so happy that I got to work at a company where I truly believed in their power and potential. The phrase “there’s magic at Mautic” had been thrown around a lot, but for what probably won’t be the last time, I believe there is definitely magic at Mautic. 

